T02TD1968E:107a-1: krishna ya m'a ri mandala stu te n'a ma /
T02TD1968E:107a-3: gshin rje gshed nag po'i dkyil 'khor gyi bstod pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1968E:107a-4: bcom ldan 'das gshin rje'i gshed nag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1968E:107a-5: ts'a rtsi k'a sogs byams sogs pas //
T02TD1968E:107a-6: 'khor lo'i gtso bo skul bar byed //
T02TD1968E:107a-7: rdo rje glu yi ngo nyid du //
T02TD1968E:107a-8: phun tshogs nyams 'bral mthong nas ni //
T02TD1968E:107a-9: khu ba'i gzugs ni yongs gyur nas //
T02TD1968E:107a-10: mam sngon nyi ma las byung ba //
T02TD1968E:107a-11: mi bzad khro bcas mdog sngon po //
T02TD1968E:107a-12: rus pa'i rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1968E:107a-13: rva rno 'bar zhing spu re skya //
T02TD1968E:107a-14: rmig pas brko zhing 'jigs sbyin pas //
T02TD1968E:107a-15: ma he yi ni rgyab gnas pa //
T02TD1968E:107a-16: rdo rje sngon po 'od dang bcas //
T02TD1968E:107a-17: sa bon bcas pa dang nyid kyis //
T02TD1968E:107a-18: ma lus dus ni 'jigs byas nas //
T02TD1968E:107a-19: bdag nyid la ni yang dag bsdus //
T02TD1968E:107a-21: ma he rdo rje'i rnal 'byor te //
T02TD1968E:107a-22: rnam shes phung po rnam dag las //
T02TD1968E:107a-23: dkyil 'khor gtso bo gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1968E:107a-25: 'od zer drag po spros pas skrod //
T02TD1968E:107a-26: drag po mun 'dra'i gzugs drag po //
T02TD1968E:107a-27: 'gro ba kun gyi nyon mongs pa'i //
T02TD1968E:107a-28: dri ma bsdus pas nag po nyid //
T02TD1968E:107a-30: gshin rje des 'dul gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1968E:107b-1: des na khro bo chen po'o //
T02TD1968E:107b-3: mche ba shin tu gtsigs pa ste //
T02TD1968E:107b-4: smin ma sma ra mgo skyes ser //
T02TD1968E:107b-5: g-yon brkyang ba yi gnas pa yis //
T02TD1968E:107b-6: 'jig rten dran pa med par byed //
T02TD1968E:107b-7: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum nyid //
T02TD1968E:107b-8: rnam par dag pas zhal gsum ste //
T02TD1968E:107b-9: rtsa ba'i zhal ni nag po che //
T02TD1968E:107b-10: g-yas pa zla ba'i 'od dang ldan //
T02TD1968E:107b-11: g-yon pa khrag dang rab tu 'dra //
T02TD1968E:107b-12: rdo rje rgyan gyi rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1968E:107b-13: thung zhing gsus pa 'phyang la sbom //
T02TD1968E:107b-14: mgo bo'i phreng bas rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1968E:107b-15: pha rol phyin drug yongs su ni //
T02TD1968E:107b-16: rdzogs par bsgoms pas phyag drug ste //
T02TD1968E:107b-17: sems can dag ni thams cad kyi //
T02TD1968E:107b-18: ji snyed sdig pa yi ni las //
T02TD1968E:107b-19: de gcod gri gug g-yas pas bsnams //
T02TD1968E:107b-20: bde ba skyong ba nyid kyi ni //
T02TD1968E:107b-21: g-yon gyi phyag na thod pa bsnams //
T02TD1968E:107b-22: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa nyid kyi ni //
T02TD1968E:107b-23: nyid mtshungs shes rab kyis 'khyud cing //
T02TD1968E:107b-24: bde bar 'khyud cing gzhan don 'dod lhan cig skyes pa'i ngo bo nyid //
T02TD1968E:107b-25: g-yas pa'i phyag gi lhag ma la //
T02TD1968E:107b-26: rdo rjes ser sna la sogs 'joms //
T02TD1968E:107b-27: nyon mongs dgra rnams rnam 'joms pas //
T02TD1968E:107b-28: ral gri 'bar ba bsnams pa ste //
T02TD1968E:107b-29: g-yon pa'i phyag gi lhag ma la //
T02TD1968E:107b-30: gtub cing sbyong ba'i 'khor lo dang //
T02TD1968E:107b-31: skyon gyis ma gos chu skyes bsdams //
T02TD1968E:107b-32: zhe sdang nyon mongs 'joms mdzad pas //
T02TD1968E:107b-33: sprul gyi dbang pos rgyan du byas //
T02TD1968E:107b-34: klu rgyal sngon po dga' bo yis //
T02TD1968E:107b-35: skra bcings shin tu 'jigs par byed //
T02TD1968E:107b-36: taksha ka klu dmar po yis //
T02TD1968E:107b-37: rna cha gdub skor byas pas 'jigs //
T02TD1968E:107b-38: rigs ldan khra bos dpung rgyan te //
T02TD1968E:107b-39: dung skyong zhes pa'i klu de ni //
T02TD1968E:107b-40: ser po lag pa'i gdu bur byas //
T02TD1968E:107b-41: padma dkar pos do shal byas //
T02TD1968E:107b-42: karko ta ni ljang gu ste //
T02TD1968E:107b-43: se ral kha ru byas pas mdzes //
T02TD1968E:107b-44: bdud rtsi mdog dang 'dra ba'i klu //
T02TD1968E:107b-45: nor rgyas bus ni ska rags byas //
T02TD1968E:107b-46: padma zla ba ltar dkar mdog / padma chen po rkang gdub yin //
T02TD1968E:107b-47: kun kyang phut sgra drag po sgrogs //
T02TD1968E:107b-48: lce gnyis mche ba'i phreng ba can //
T02TD1968E:107b-49: chos sku'i rang bzhin nyid phyir du //
T02TD1968E:107b-50: longs spyod rdzogs dang sprul pa yis //
T02TD1968E:107b-51: gzugs su mdzad pa'i rang bzhin te //
T02TD1968E:107b-52: chos dbyings ye shes rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1968E:108a-2: gzugs kyi phung po rnam dag pas //
T02TD1968E:108a-3: rtag pa phyag drug dkar po ste //
T02TD1968E:108a-4: rtsa ba'i zhal ni dkar po la //
T02TD1968E:108a-5: g-yas pa gnag cing g-yon pa dmar //
T02TD1968E:108a-6: g-yas pa 'khor lo ral gri phyag / g-yon pa rin chen chu skyes 'dzin //
T02TD1968E:108a-7: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor mnyam par gnon //
T02TD1968E:108a-8: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
T02TD1968E:108a-10: lho ru ma dang rin chen las //
T02TD1968E:108a-11: tshor ba'i phung po rnam dag pas //
T02TD1968E:108a-12: byung ba phra ma gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1968E:108a-13: btso ma gser gyi mdog 'dra ma //
T02TD1968E:108a-14: rtsa ba'i zhal ni ser po ste //
T02TD1968E:108a-15: g-yas pa gnag cing g-yon pa dkar //
T02TD1968E:108a-16: g-yas na rin chen ral gri bsnams //
T02TD1968E:108a-17: g-yon na 'khor lo chu skyes nyid //
T02TD1968E:108a-18: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
T02TD1968E:108a-20: me dang padma las byung ba //
T02TD1968E:108a-21: nub tu 'dod chags rdo rje can //
T02TD1968E:108a-22: 'du shes phung po rnam dag nyid //
T02TD1968E:108a-24: rtsa ba'i zhal ni dmar la gdangs //
T02TD1968E:108a-25: g-yas pa gnag cing g-yon pa dkar //
T02TD1968E:108a-26: g-yas na padma ral gri bsnams //
T02TD1968E:108a-27: phyag g-yon rin chen 'khor lo ste //
T02TD1968E:108a-28: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis //
T02TD1968E:108a-30: da dang ral gri las byung ba //
T02TD1968E:108a-31: 'du byed phung po rnam dag pas //
T02TD1968E:108a-32: byang du phrag dog gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1968E:108a-34: rtsa ba'i zhal ni ljang gu ste //
T02TD1968E:108a-35: g-yas pa gnag cing g-yon pa dkar //
T02TD1968E:108a-36: g-yas na ral gri 'khor lo bsnams //
T02TD1968E:108a-37: mdzes pa'i nor bu padma las //
T02TD1968E:108a-38: bya ba nan tan ye shes kyis //
T02TD1968E:108a-40: khro bo'i gzugs can thams cad kyang //
T02TD1968E:108a-41: zhe sdang gshin rje'i mtshan nyid mtshungs //
T02TD1968E:108a-42: de dag pa yi phyag gnyis la //
T02TD1968E:108a-43: gri gug dang ni thod pa bsnams //
T02TD1968E:108a-44: rang gi shes rab lus dag dang //
T02TD1968E:108a-45: bde ba'i dngos po gnyis med rol //
T02TD1968E:108a-46: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor mnyam par gnon //
T02TD1968E:108a-47: rdo rje rtsibs kyi rtsar bzhugs shing //
T02TD1968E:108a-49: sems can don mdzad phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1968E:108a-50: shar sgor ya dang tho ba las //
T02TD1968E:108a-51: byung ba sngon po'i gzugs can te //
T02TD1968E:108a-52: 'jig tshogs lta ba rnam dag nyid //
T02TD1968E:108b-0: g-yas dkar g-yon dmar dbus @108b sngon zhal //
T02TD1968E:108b-1: g-yas na tho ba ral gri 'dzin //
T02TD1968E:108b-2: nor bu mchog dang padma g-yon //
T02TD1968E:108b-3: tho ba zhe sdang gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1968E:108b-4: brtson 'grus stobs kyi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1968E:108b-6: tsa dang dbyug pa las byung lhor //
T02TD1968E:108b-7: dbyug pa gshin rje gshed mdog dkar //
T02TD1968E:108b-8: mthar 'dzin lta ba rnam dag nyid //
T02TD1968E:108b-9: g-yas sngo g-yon dmar dbus dkar zhal //
T02TD1968E:108b-10: g-yas na dbyug pa ral gri bsnams //
T02TD1968E:108b-11: chu skyes 'khor lo g-yon gyi phyag //
T02TD1968E:108b-12: dbang po'i stobs kyi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1968E:108b-14: ni dang padma las byung nub //
T02TD1968E:108b-15: padma gshin rje gshed nyid ni //
T02TD1968E:108b-16: log par lta ba rnam dag nyid //
T02TD1968E:108b-17: g-yas gnag g-yo dkar dbus zhal dmar //
T02TD1968E:108b-18: g-yas na padma ral gri bsnams //
T02TD1968E:108b-19: phyag g-yon rin chen 'khor lo ste //
T02TD1968E:108b-20: dran pa'i stobs kyi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1968E:108b-22: ra dang ral gri las byung ba //
T02TD1968E:108b-23: byang du ral gri gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1968E:108b-24: lta ba mchog 'dzin rnam dag nyid //
T02TD1968E:108b-25: g-yas gnag g-yon dkar dbus ljang zhal //
T02TD1968E:108b-26: g-yas na ral gri 'khor lo bsnams //
T02TD1968E:108b-27: mdzes pa'i nor bu padma g-yon //
T02TD1968E:108b-28: ting 'dzin stobs kyi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1968E:108b-30: kun kyang sprul gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1968E:108b-34: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa //
T02TD1968E:108b-35: mche ba gtsigs shing 'jigs pa'i zhal //
T02TD1968E:108b-36: gri gug thod pa 'dzin par mdzad //
T02TD1968E:108b-38: mi gnas sgrol mdzad phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1968E:108b-39: sna tshogs rdo rje'i mtshams bzhi ru //
T02TD1968E:108b-40: lha mo zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD1968E:108b-41: shar lhor dza dang 'khor lo las //
T02TD1968E:108b-42: lha mo rdo rje ts'a rtsi kla //
T02TD1968E:108b-43: sa khams rnam dag thabs kyi bdag / sgeg mo dkar mo cher khro ma //
T02TD1968E:108b-44: gti mug gshin rje gshed dang mtshungs //
T02TD1968E:108b-45: byams pa chen po'i ngo bo yis //
T02TD1968E:108b-47: de bzhin lho rus dang ni //
T02TD1968E:108b-48: rdo rje las byung rdo rje phag / chu khams rnam dag stobs kyi bdag / khro zhing phag gi gdong pa can //
T02TD1968E:109a-2: snying rje chen po'i ngo bo yis //
T02TD1968E:109a-4: nub dang byang gi mtshams su ni //
T02TD1968E:109a-5: do skyes gtso mo rab tu dmar //
T02TD1968E:109a-6: me khams rnam dag smon lam bdag / rab tu zhi ba'i dbyangs can ma //
T02TD1968E:109a-7: 'dod chags gshin rje gshed dang mtshungs //
T02TD1968E:109a-8: dga' ba chen po'i ngo bo yis //
T02TD1968E:109a-10: byang dang shar gyi mtshams su ni //
T02TD1968E:109a-11: ru skyes goo r'i ljang gu ma //
T02TD1968E:109a-12: rlung khams rnam dag ye shes bdag /'jigs byed phrag dog gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1968E:109a-13: gzugs dang mtshan ma mchog tu 'dzin //
T02TD1968E:109a-14: btang snyoms chen po'i ngo bo yis //
T02TD1968E:109a-16: mtha' gnyis rab tu sgrol mdzad de //
T02TD1968E:109a-17: rang rig gtso la phan 'dogs shing //
T02TD1968E:109a-18: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med bdag / lha mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1968E:109a-19: mtshams bzhir na yo ni ra las //
T02TD1968E:109a-20: phyi rol gzugs rdzogs rnam dag las //
T02TD1968E:109a-21: dkyil 'khor du ni thod pa gnas //
T02TD1968E:109a-22: chos dbyings kun du 'gro ba'i phyir //
T02TD1968E:109a-23: bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga yis bkang //
T02TD1968E:109a-24: de ltar mi mthun tshogs bcom nas //
T02TD1968E:109a-25: rab tu rgyal ba'i rtags mtshan nyid //
T02TD1968E:109a-26: thod pa bzhi yi ngo bo ste //
T02TD1968E:109a-27: bde ba chen po phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1968E:109a-28: bsod nams ye shes chen po las byung sku gsung ye shes lngar ldan 'jigs gzugs la //
T02TD1968E:109a-29: bdag nyid dad pa'i mthu yis sku yi yon tan tsam mthong dad pa'i dbyangs kyis bstod pa yis //
T02TD1968E:109a-30: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor dong rnams rnam rtog rlung gis phyogs bcur g-yengs pas sdug bsngal rnams //
T02TD1968E:109a-31: skye rgas na 'chi spangs nas 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las rgal bla med byang chub thob par shog / slob dpon dpal 'dzin gyi dgongs pa nye bar bsdus pa las //
T02TD1968E:109a-32: gshin rje gshed nag po'i dkyil 'khor gyi bstod pa /
T02TD1968E:109a-33: a'a ts'arya k'i rti'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
